---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "About";
const identity = {
  firstName: "Sarah",
  country: "Canada",
  occupation: "Technical Writer",
  hobbies: ["Photography", "Birdwatching", "Baseball"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React", "Astro", "Writing Docs"];

const happy = true;
const finished = true;
const goal = 3;
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h2>About Me</h2>

  <p>
    Hello! I'm a Full-Stack Developer with a deep passion for building scalable
    web applications. With expertise in Java (Spring Boot) and modern frontend
    frameworks like React and Vue, I spend my days bridging the gap between
    robust backend logic and intuitive user interfaces.
  </p>

  <p>
    I created this blog to document my journey through the evolving AI
    landscape—specifically how tools like Cursor and Claude Code are reshaping
    the way we write code. Whether you're here to solve a tricky Java bug or to
    optimize your React performance, I hope you find my technical deep-dives
    helpful.
  </p>

  <p>
    When I'm not coding, I'm usually exploring the latest in AI image generation
    or fine-tuning my development workflow.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
